<h4 id="css">CSS</h4>
<p>To add CSS to the stylesheet, you have to call one of the functions defined in <a href="/Sources/HyperSwift/API/CSS/CSSExtensions.swift">CSSExtensions.swift</a>.</p>

<p>If an element has a class name, the styles will automatically be added to <a href="/Sources/HyperSwift/API/CSS/CSSStyleSheet.swift">CSSStyleSheet.swift</a>’s stylesheet.</p>

<p>Calling <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.generateStyleSheet()</code> on <a href="/Sources/HyperSwift/API/CSS/CSSStyleSheet.swift">CSSStyleSheet.swift</a> will return a string containing the stylesheet.</p>

<h4 id="examples">Examples</h4>
<p>HyperSwift is being used on <a href="https://www.garrepi.dev">garrepi.dev</a> as we speak!</p>

<p>Checkout the source code <a href="https://github.com/johngarrett/garrepi.dev/">here</a>.</p>
